<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <title>Email : for activate account</title>
    <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <style type="text/css">
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            min-width: 100%;
            font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
            font-size: 1rem;
            line-height: 1.5;
            background-color: #fafafa;
            color: #222222;

        }

        a {
            color: #000;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 700;
            line-height: 1.25;
            margin-top: 0;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        p {
            margin-top: 0;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
        }

        table td {
            vertical-align: top;
        }

        .email-wrapper {
            max-width: 600pz;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .email-header {
            background-color: #0070f3;
            padding: 24px;
            color: #fff;
        }

        .email-body {
            padding: 24px;
            background-color: #fff;
        }

        .email-footer {
            background-color: #f6f6f6;
            padding: 24px;
        }

        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #0070f3;
            color: #fff;
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 700;
            text-align: center;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            border-radius: 4px;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="email-wrapper">
        <div class="email-header">
            <h1>Welcome to LMS</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="email-body">
            <p>Hello <%= user.name %>
            </p>
            <p>Thank you for registering weth LMS . to activate your account, please use the following activation
                code: </p>
            <h2>
                <%= activationCode %>
            </h2>
            <p>Please enter this code on the activation page within the next 5 miniutes</p>
            <p>If you did not register for a webBlog's account, plase ignore this email.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="email-footer">
            <p>If you have any questions , please don't hesitate to contact us at <a
                    href="kumaekunal18@gmail.com">kumaekunal18@gmail.com</a></p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>